** This software is far from complete and will contain many bugs!! **

The goals of this project are:

* To provide a complete retrosheet parser/importer
* To provide a complete lahman importer
* To provide a complete MLB pitch FX importer
* To store to one of many database vendors
* To provide a web interface to all data
* to provide an easy map/reduce way to generate statistics